comments.content: Help me on identifying font from image file
I was going to say Linoscript but it's actually [French Script](http://web.archive.org/web/20150419154250/http:/www.fonts.com/FindFonts/detail.htm?pid=203226)
thanks a lot praitsidis for helping me. I got French Script fonts.
